  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomised controlled double blinded clinical trial to determine the antiemetic
      efficacy and safety of either 8 mg of dexamethasone or normal saline (placebo) given 1 hour
      before induction of either spinal or general anaesthesia in 2 arms (of 150 each).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
